casebody.data:
Serajul HAQUE, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 16-6829. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 9, 2017. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
